{"type": "article", "id": 26178, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-29T07:22:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26917, "name": "HIRA"}, {"id": 23746, "name": "Goat Story"}, {"id": 26918, "name": "PURITAAN"}, {"id": 26919, "name": "560G"}, {"id": 26920, "name": "Altor"}, {"id": 26921, "name": "Siya"}, {"id": 26959, "name": "June"}, {"id": 26922, "name": "Miles Endo"}, {"id": 23851, "name": "Backbone Branding"}, {"id": 26923, "name": "Anze Miklavec"}, {"id": 26924, "name": "Norbert Pap"}, {"id": 26960, "name": "Frank Rettenbacher"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607183857rgcMxJQO2Bo7zidC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>HIRA by Miles Endo</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Miles Endo 是 <a href=\"http://www.studioendo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">STUDIO ENDO</a> 的一名设计师，他的父母都是日本太鼓手。以此为灵感，他设计了这套名为 <a href=\"http://api.viglink.com/api/click?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_146182645604014&amp;key=6ab1d62aaf9dbafae96546ba3ca1b2ac&amp;libId=injwmbx50100x1tt000DL1ey6e7yoscvks&amp;loc=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Fhira-collection-inspired-japanese-taiko-drums%2F&amp;v=1&amp;out=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.studioendo.com%2Fcollections%2Fhira-lighting-series&amp;title=Furnishings%20Inspired%20by%20Taiko%20Drums%20-%20Design%20Milk&amp;txt=HIRA\">HIRA</a> 的家具包含了一系列灯具和媒体柜，采用铜和仿乌木作为主要的制作材料，传递出了日系的简约和典雅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021122531J7tbLIQYa5wrZg4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112253KMUt0LZcrm96BSJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112254OKvNUFWjd1Zly369.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021122546K3RzAVcUbEHoN5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112254F1jZhAxo3yQwkuCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112255hRBw4Fcl6Ep5V3oY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>GOAT STORY by Anze Miklavec</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这不是号角，而是由 <a href=\"http://www.goat-story.com/\">Anze Miklavec</a> 设计的一款名为 GOAT STORY 的咖啡杯。之所以选择山羊角形状，也有它的渊源——根据传说，一位牧羊人发现他的山羊吃了一种植物的种子之后变得非常兴奋，继而发现了咖啡。如果不想拿着杯子，只要将把手卸下倒置放在平面上，就能把杯子支撑起来了。不仅趣味十足，也兼备了实用性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112255t8S0ZTPWgXxVilry.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112256Kvwlh45YTBisbH1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112256lNbDPHQ82dv076tp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112257zwunM2ScjH87tLer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021122577wotpCLSRM6EygvH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021122589agHY3BzlqSMhyvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>PURITAAN by Norbert Pap</h2>\n<p class=\"\">设计师 Norbert Pap 取材于 MacBook 电脑包，设计出了这款贯彻了极简风格的皮革背包 PURITAAN。黑色皮料搭配金属圆钉，在维持低调的同时又透露出了时尚的气息，无论是通勤还是日常使用都很合适。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112258INuliRgnLvHQO9pj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112259rgTxpDitFo1fYyaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112300kJnzGpNPdRSY7gH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112300nOwQbF2oRJGcv1yf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112300T5YHPOIemqGgxyjh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>560G by Altor</h2>\n<p class=\"\">如果你打算换一个自行车锁，这款由双人设计组合 Altor 打造的 560G 是个不错的选择。它由五级钛合金制作而成，而重量（正如其名）仅为 560 克，是目前市面上最轻的高安全性自行车锁。目前它正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1282151086/560g\">Kickstarter</a> 上展开众筹，最低价为 150 美金。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112301jtsUFEmdw14cpV9u.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112301vxywangQYz2jmf4o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112302em6gTXxbAfDLwad0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112303L7MB9Y41fE2QRW6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112303wdqXCQHsRVD3k2pJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112304V3B87JGhZjUCm4sn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>June by Frank Rettenbacher</h2>\n<p class=\"\">由奥地利设计师 <a href=\"http://www.frankrettenbacher.com/\">Frank Rettenbacher</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.zanotta.it/en/\">ZANOTTA</a> 所设计 June 系列是一组椅背看上去像是悬浮在座位上的椅子，简洁的几何造型以及不同材质之间的结合让人眼前一亮。设计环节中最大的挑战就是如何让椅背不借助可见的螺丝钉与座椅接合在一起，Rettenbacher 在和技术团队经过激烈的沟通之后最终确定了现在所看到的这种隐蔽的接合方法。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112304ikaorEeJCcKOMnPT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021123053muokFQdb8OGHtfY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112305xYIXBPKul2V4J8UC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112306FGUuyBafj1nw9qXD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112306MXdxosSNZh7bpima.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112307qClZLhzIrYakxEA0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Siya by Backbone Branding</h2>\n<p class=\"\">在到底该如何表现果汁的新鲜程度上，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://backbonebranding.com/\">Backbone Branding</a> 有一套自己的想法：这个为 Siya 系列果汁所设计的包装，好像就是一个真实水果被放在了果汁瓶上。巧妙的弧线造型配合精心策划后实际拍摄出的照片，使得它在众多果汁包装中脱颖而出，很好地反映出了“天然”的感觉，像是锁住了盛夏的味道。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112307rh4MA82ZL3P9aGu5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112308Nny3j0UpBQ2gXui7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112308LyfZuXzEO9pY1MV0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112309ksBE6jwUhxVYcD0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112309pEuYrX9RALcoQmBw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112310fGLKnYRZIteUF0rx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.47476341\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}